### Get all tasks
GET http://localhost:5000/api/tasks

### Create a new task
POST http://localhost:5000/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "text": "Build the backend engine"
}

### Update a task (Replace <ID> with an actual ID from the GET request)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/<ID_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "completed": true
}

### Delete a task (Replace <ID> with an actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/tasks/<ID_HERE>